summary:
Pokémon Go Adding New Item that Lets Players Switch Teams Once a Year 

Early on in Pokémon Go, players are given one of three...
caption:
Pokémon Go Adding New Item that Lets Players Switch Teams Once a Year

Early on in Pokémon Go, players are given one of three options to choose their desired team. For those who may have decided their choice wasn’t their favorite, no worries! As the latest update will allow players to purchase an item to switch this team, but can only be used once a year. 

Check it!
